description100.description: Washington (8-3, 5-3 Big Ten) and No. 6 Oregon (10-1, 7-1) end their slates with a rivalry matchup.

description1000.description: The Huskies (8-3, 5-3 Big Ten) and No. 6 Ducks (10-1, 7-1) end their slates with a rivalry matchup. Oregon toppled Washington 49-21 last year, snapping a three-game series skid that included a 34-31 loss in the most recent Pac-12 title game in 2023.

description100.description: TCU (7-4, 4-4 Big 12) and Cincinnati (7-4, 5-3) put their finishing touches on the regular season.

description1000.description: The Horned Frogs (7-4, 4-4 Big 12) and Bearcats (7-4, 5-3) put the finishing touches on their regular-season slates. In 2024, TCU spoiled Cincinnati's bid for bowl eligibility with a 20-13 victory in the first meeting between the schools in 20 years.
